Including Plots

You can also embed plots, for example:

The above plot shows the total number of persons associated with each mission from 1884-1887. An interesting feature of the above graphs is that the total number of missionaries associated with Turkey far exceeded the number of missionaries associated with any other geographic region.

ggplot(abcfm_missionaries_native, aes(Report_year))+ geom_bar()

The plot above shows the number of native pastors named in ABCFM annual reports.

Overall, the data has a few major problems. It is not tidy enough and I need to add gender as a variable. It is also tricky to plot data for each specific mission for each year, which is a problem that will need to be resolved before any further analysis can move forward. The lack of continus variables aside from year also presents a problem and it may be beneficial to include total numbers of mission congregations in a separate table to join to this one.
